 	<li><strong>Collectibles</strong>: Explore the whitespace hub to unlock hidden music, artwork, and lore entries.</li>
</ul>
These additions add hours of replayability, ensuring the game remains engaging long after the credits roll.
<h3>Graphics and Soundtrack</h3>
